Image module

Description:    Image  module     providing  basic     image   loading
functionality. At the moment   there is only one implementation  using
SDL and SDL_image to load: BMP, PNM (PPM/PGM/PBM), XPM, LBM, PCX, GIF,
JPEG, PNG, TGA, and TIFF formats.

Security:
Depends on security of SDL and SDL_image.

Module dependencies:
Image -> Video (todo: this dependency should be removed)

Native library dependencies:

Image -> libSDL
Image -> libSDL_image

Constructors:

//! return image object constructed from image data
Image(data)
